## Frontend (Vite) Environment Variables

# Base path for the app. For Vercel and local dev use '/'.
VITE_BASE_PATH=/

# Absolute API base the frontend will call.
# Local dev uses Vite proxy (/api) so this can be omitted locally.
# For production (Render backend): set to your Render URL with /api suffix.
# Example:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://rrnagar-coming-soon.onrender.com/api

# Origin of backend for constructing absolute URLs to assets like /uploads/*
# Example:
# VITE_BACKEND_ORIGIN=https://rrnagar-coming-soon.onrender.com

# Canonical GitHub repo URLs used by deployment scripts and CI
GITHUB_FRONTEND_REPO=https://github.com/tulasiprasadk/rrnagarfinal-frontend
GITHUB_BACKEND_REPO=https://github.com/tulasiprasadk/rrnagarfinal-backend
